@startuml state-assignment-attempt
title State - AssignmentAttempt (QUIZ)

[*] --> IN_PROGRESS : POST /api/students/assignments/{id}/attempts/start
IN_PROGRESS --> PAUSED_BY_TEACHER : POST /api/teachers/assignments/{id}/attempts/override (PAUSE)
PAUSED_BY_TEACHER --> IN_PROGRESS : override (RESUME)
IN_PROGRESS --> TERMINATED_TEACHER : override (TERMINATE)
IN_PROGRESS --> SUBMITTED : POST /api/students/assignments/{id}/submit
SUBMITTED --> [*]
TERMINATED_TEACHER --> [*]

@enduml